                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColor};")
                                    | Through this incredibly challenging year, we’ve drawn inspiration from the strength of the osteopathic profession. We are deeply moved by the thousands of DOs across the country who have bravely and selflessly cared for the sickest of patients day after day. And our hearts are filled with growing anticipation for the relief and recovery we hope 2021 will bring.

