                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColor};")
                                    | This holiday season, we celebrate the collective contributions of more than 151,000 DOs and medical students who are making an impact in communities large and small. And we renew our unyielding commitment to advance and uplift the osteopathic profession and support the work you do each day.

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColor};")
                                    | Thank you for choosing the AOA as your professional home. No matter how you celebrate the holidays this year, we wish you peace, love and joy.

